Class Point3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment5.Point3D

  • public class Point3D
extends java.lang.Object
    Point3D is a public class that has 3 integer variables that correspond to a point in a 3 dimensional space. It also has accessor methods for returning the points to another program.
